A question that every teenager or oh well every young adult asks themselves almost every night before going to sleep or before every day dreaming session! I've haven't really figured out "Who I'm?" but I can speak for things that I think I've figured out. My friends call me extrovert which probably is true, however I do enjoy my alone self time (quite a lot of time!). I was born when creativity and intelligence hooked up for a while Well, I'm can get really creative I won't shy away saying that I like to study, that 100% true but is that the only thing that I like to do, probably not! I live by lists, schedules and pri On a random day, you'll find me sticking my eyes to the laptop screen either coding, attending online lectures (why even?), reading blogs, reading research papers (oh not that much but yes!) However, if you manage to see me without my laptop, I'd be reading some nice book Mental disorders have always been something on the top of my "to-do hobbies" list
Can you imagine a CS nerdy girl being interested in real estate? Hell yeah! I enjoy watching beautiful mansions, buildings and specially the ones that are smaller in areas but transformed with beautiful architecture to some amazing looking and full utility spaces! You can checkout: NeverTooSmall (unpaid promotion, please pay?). I wish to own one of these and, whenever I'm sad, need some space, have a mental breakdown or have an amazing idea to work on, I'll escape there for few days and come back happy again! (So, if you end up marrying me which you obviously won't, you know where to find me xD)
If you want to pick me up for a date (which probably you wouldn't if you're here but...), remember that I love quite places, prefer beachy locations, always up for long drives and long walks, oh and would love if you'd take me out to a nice shopping place! (See that's what you do with lack of a nice tinder profile!)
